	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Hi hi, <anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />c'était le fun, non? <anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Merci
